# ============================================
# PRODUCTION SECURITY NOTES
# ============================================
# 1. Generate APP_KEY: php artisan key:generate
# 2. Change all passwords above - these are examples only
# 3. Use strong passwords (min 32 characters, mixed case, numbers, symbols)
# 4. Never commit .env file to version control
# 5. Rotate passwords regularly (every 90 days)
# 6. Use environment-specific secrets management in production
# 7. Enable SESSION_ENCRYPT=true and SESSION_SECURE_COOKIE=true
# 8. Configure proper MAIL settings for production (SendGrid/Mailgun/SES)
# 9. Set LOG_LEVEL=error in production
# 10. Use Redis password protection
# 11. Configure SSL certificates: make ssl-setup
# 12. Set MEDIA_USE_SERVER_STORAGE=true for production
# 13. Use Redis for SESSION_DRIVER and CACHE_STORE
# 14. Set SANCTUM_STATEFUL_DOMAINS to actual production domains only
# 15. Remove localhost from SANCTUM_STATEFUL_DOMAINS in production